name: FEME 6T6
description:
Tron revival, 2 motorbike rider girls face-off, cool helmet skins, power ups, awesome visual effects.

Player 1: WASD, Space, Left Ctrl

Player 2: Arrows, Right Ctrl, Right Alt (or Left and Right Mouse)

GAME DEVELOPERS

A group of professionals from ESNE University deciding to contribute to their Game Jam, out-of-competition:

Noel Pradana - Artist

Luis Sagastibelza - Producer

Silvia Osoro - Programmer

Marcos Maqueda - Programmer and Technical Artist

Angel Luis Marinas - Programmer and Designer

Jorge Aranda - Sound Designer
